.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 344, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadako_Sasaki\", \"score\": 0.9981520911401377, \"rank\": 0.0015802348150165562, \"text\": \"Sasaki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadako_Sasaki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sadako_Sasaki\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9775783067096001, \"rank\": 0.02293295742615295, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 399, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oksana_Livach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oksana Livach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oksana_Livach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oksana_Livach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh became the first-ever wrestler from India to compete for the Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 484, \"end\": 489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9124170756379112, \"rank\": 0.056210770354537504, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her victory has been drawing praise from the different corners of the country and also from her family which has produced some top-notch wrestlers.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 670, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Babita, a former wrestler, congratulated Vinesh for making the country proud.\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.78388500317112e-22, \"text\": \"Babita\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today is a proud day for the country.\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a very happy day that Vinesh has reached the final,\\\" Babita told ANI.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.78388500317112e-22, \"text\": \"Babita\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The hard work that Vinesh and her supporting staff have done, everyone made a contribution in a player winning the medal for the country.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I congratulate Vinesh as she is the first women wrestler to reach the final at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her decision to fight in the 50 kg category, was a good move.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has won all her medals in this category.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a suitable category for her.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1241, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My father dreamed that our daughters would win a medal at the Olympics, today it's going to be fulfilled,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#WATCH| Double Olympic medalist Manu Bhaker shows her medal as she arrives in Delhi after her historic performance in#ParisOlympics2024She won bronze medals in Women's 10m Air Pistol & the 10m Air Pistol Mixed team event.pic.twitter.com/5dylr6Zimv  - ANI (@ANI)August 7, 2024      'She's daughter of the country': Vinesh's mother  Vinesh's mother Premlata, in an exclusive conversation with CNN News18, expressed that her daughter shall return home with a gold medal.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manu Bhaker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\"}, {\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9986706494522983, \"rank\": 0.0013301110878094064, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}, {\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9997350987